{"type":"text","timestamp":1775859537308,"sessionID":"ses_28689d81bffeoSw6AycaOV3rq3","part":{"id":"prt_d7979f6ce001yr0GnHrSTCtk1j","messageID":"msg_d7979d8c9001CHJgc7hIHYh1Po","sessionID":"ses_28689d81bffeoSw6AycaOV3rq3","type":"text","text":"I've successfully created the `proposal.md` file for AR-010 — Router 会话管理 (Router Session Management) at `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md`.\n\nThe proposal includes:\n\n1. **Purpose** — Four primary responsibilities: Session Resolution, Session Lifecycle, Session Affinity, and Resource Integration via client-go\n\n2. **Scope** — In-scope items (session creation, resolution, lifecycle, affinity, CRD integration via client-go) and out-of-scope items (HTTP proxy, JWT, TLS from AR-009)\n\n3. **Design** — Detailed sections covering:\n   - File layout (8 new files)\n   - Type definitions (`SessionManager`, `SessionInfo`, `sessionManager`, `RuntimeClient`)\n   - Session resolution flow diagram\n   - Session creation implementation\n   - Session affinity routing\n   - Lifecycle management with cleanup\n   - Kubernetes client-go integration for `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` CRDs\n   - Prometheus metrics\n   - Configuration defaults\n   - Error handling\n\n4. **Impact Analysis** — ~1,230 lines of new code across 8 files\n\n5. **Alternatives Considered** — 5 alternatives with detailed rejection rationale\n\n6. **Dependencies** — Including the generated `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` for CRD access\n\n7. **Verification** — Test commands for unit and integration tests\n\n8. **References** — Links to session-routing design, client-go spec, AR-009, and related documentation","time":{"start":1775859537305,"end":1775859537305}}}
